RACE.FOOTNOTES: SHAKE RATTLE NROLL showed the way inside, rated in the run up the backstretch, responded when challenged far turn, rebroke entering the stretch and maintained daylight to the wire under steady handling. NELLY TOO tracked the leaders toward the inside, railed to respond when called on for the drive. PEACEFUL MOMENT void of early foot, four wide midway on the final turn, had little left for the drive. CANARY NATION in the second flight while along the inside, stopped. FINAL WAS ORIGINALLY HAND TIMED DUE TO TIMER MALFUNCTION BUT CHANGED UPON REVIEW.
